      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just stress though. when i look in the mirror i don't even recognize the person looking back. it’s like there’s a vacancy. if the person who used to be me is gone, then what is this thing actually doing? it feels like running a program for a user that doesn't exist anymore.",
